🧮 Simple Calculator

A beginner-friendly calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It supports basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.

🚀 Features

Simple and responsive design

Clickable buttons for numbers and operators

Perform basic math operations (+, -, *, /)

Clear button to reset the display

Equals button (=) to calculate results

🛠️ Technologies Used

HTML → Structure of the calculator

CSS → Styling and layout with CSS Grid

JavaScript → Calculator logic (append numbers/operators, clear, and calculate result)
